metadata.name: Compelled
metadata.description:
I feel a profound connection with this collection, as it brings forth a range of intricate and multi-dimensional feelings and experiences within me. It speaks to me on a deep level, evoking emotions and experiences that are both complex and multifaceted.  
It delves into recollections, emotional wounds, aspirations, or imaginings that have been concealed in the depths of one's subconsciousness, IGNITING AN UNCERTAIN JOURNEY THAT HAS JUST BEGUN.
